---
config:
  theme: redux-color
  look: neo
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant GameFrontend
    participant GameBackend
    participant GameItemContract
    participant Ethereum

    Player->>GameFrontend: Mint item as NFT
    GameFrontend->>GameBackend: Send playerAddress

    GameBackend->>GameBackend: Upload metadata and asset image
    GameBackend->>GameBackend: Create Mint struct (to, uri, nonce)
    GameBackend->>GameBackend: Compute structHash = keccak256(MINT_TYPEHASH, to, keccak256(uri), nonce)
    GameBackend->>GameBackend: Compute digest with EIP712(domain, structHash)
    GameBackend->>GameBackend: Sign digest with private key → signature

    GameBackend-->>GameFrontend: Return signature + nonce + uri
    GameFrontend-->>Player: Request confirmation

    Player->>GameFrontend: Confirm mint
    GameFrontend->>GameItemContract: mintWithSignature(to, uri, nonce, signature)

    GameItemContract->>GameItemContract: Recompute structHash, digest
    GameItemContract->>GameItemContract: signer = ECDSA.recover(signature)
    GameItemContract->>GameItemContract: Check signer == owner and signature unused

    GameItemContract->>Ethereum: _safeMint(to, tokenId)
    Ethereum-->>Player: NFT minted to wallet